Sorry, I missed the discussion in slack.  Agree with adding producer group, this looks more versatile. And we'd better consider adding a flag to enable deduplication based on the producer group name.  If the flag is false, producers in the same group also use name-based deduplication.

If the producer group added, I think the producer with the same name but the different group can connect to the broker. Hence, the group name also needs to consider adding to the unique identifier of the producer.

